  <name>BLOUedit</name>
  <summary>Professional video editing application</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      BLOUedit is a professional-grade video editing application with advanced
      features similar to commercial software.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Multi-track timeline editing</li>
      <li>Advanced transitions and effects</li>
      <li>Text and title creation</li>
      <li>Professional color grading</li>
      <li>Audio editing and mixing</li>
      <li>Motion tracking and keyframing</li>
      <li>AI-powered editing tools (auto cutting, style transfer)</li>
      <li>Resource management</li>
      <li>Project templates</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
